#circuitbreakersg day 50

Mala Xiang Guo 麻辣香锅 (Spicy numbing stir-fry) 🤤 
Been seeing a lot ppl selling this Haichijia Sour & Spicy Noodle Have tried, it’s good, it’s not spicy but will numb ur tongue. But sour and really shiok! Very appetising.
(Go get it from ezbuy, it’s cheaper😏) Really like chewy/silky kind of noodle and decided to use Six Fortune Mung bean thread noodle for Mala xiang guo and added some Mala abalone from @imperialpremiumseafood 👍🏻👍🏻🤤🤤🤤🔥
#jxeatshome #stayhome
@thewinerysg 😍 hope u get ur craving fixed soon!!
@jxeats yes! Haha we had mala instant maggie the fastest way!
We have been craving for this!

Love the texture of mung bean noodles 😄
